text: Tihovići is a village in Vogošća municipality, near Sarajevo, Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==Population== ===Ethnic composition, 1991 census=== total: 368 * Muslims by nationality - 367 (99.72%) * others and unknown - 1 (0.27%) ==History== ==References== * Official results from the book: Ethnic composition of Bosnia-Herzegovina population, by municipalities and settlements, 1991. census, Zavod za statistiku Bosne i Hercegovine - Bilten no.234, Sarajevo 1991.
